# EXPENSE TRACKER APP 
This is a simple python based expense tracker to manage daily expenses efficiently

## About
This application helps user :
- View all expenses
- Add expenes
- Delete expenses
- Calculate total spent
- Save expenses to a file

## Features
- Menu driven interface
- Stores expenses in lists
- Saves data to a file
- Beginner-friendly and easy to modify

## Technologies used
- Python programming language

